### Test Censorship API
POST http://localhost:5083/censorship/censor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Text": "T'es trop gentil mais arrete d'etre trop chiant"
}

### Test with empty text (should return 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:5083/censorship/censor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Text": ""
}

### Test with no banned words
POST http://localhost:5083/censorship/censor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Text": "This is a clean text with no banned words."
}

### Test with different case (should be case-insensitive)
POST http://localhost:5083/censorship/censor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Text": "This contains HATE and Violence and Discriminate words."
}